# Unlike .gitignore, these ARE bundled into the deployed image — vendor
# terms permit using official architecture icons within a diagramming tool
# to represent that vendor's services (Loom's actual purpose), just not
# redistributing the icon set itself as a standalone downloadable asset
# pack, which is what committing them to the public git repo would look
# like. See src/assets/icons/README.md.
